import React from 'react'
import { Grid, Image, Header } from 'semantic-ui-react'

export default function About() {
    
    return (
        <React.Fragment>
            <Grid>
                <Grid.Column width={7}>
                    <Image src='/images/wireframe/image.png' />
                </Grid.Column>
                <Grid.Column width={9}>
                    <Header></Header>
                </Grid.Column>
            </Grid>
        </React.Fragment>
    )
}
